cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CL, cs.NE 

This paper is about visual recognition using deep neural networks and non-parametric approaches. The most likely sub-category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition), followed by cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.CL (Computation and Language), and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). The paper focuses on improving generalization, which is a common problem in computer vision and machine learning. The use of deep neural networks and non-parametric approaches is also a common theme in these sub-categories.
